{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ae3e4873-a5f6-4cfa-a1a7-29bae9c5e8f5","content":"No `SettingsPage.xaml` found in the working directory. Since there's no existing file, here's how to convert it to compiled bindings:\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to the root element pointing to your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" FontSize=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme name\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Slider Minimum=\"10\" Maximum=\"36\" Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` — this tells the XAML compiler the type of `BindingContext`, enabling compile-time validation of all `{Binding}` paths.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Typos are now build errors.** If you write `{Binding Themee}`, the compiler will emit an error like:\n   > XC0045: Member 'Themee' not found on type 'SettingsViewModel'\n\n2. **Enable warnings-as-errors** in your `.csproj` for stricter enforcement:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045;XC0022</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n3. **If you need to opt out** for a subtree (e.g., a dynamically-typed area), use `x:DataType=\"\"` to disable compiled bindings locally.\n\nThat's it — no runtime reflection, better performance, and mistyped property names fail the build instead of silently producing empty UI.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ef9620cf-c625-4ba6-a9af-1f9a3aaf603f","outputTokens":536,"requestId":"0821:1A5086:A1F2CE:BB47D5:69F2A773"},"id":"e3b2ec14-3bad-480a-8ee6-1ad66880b281","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:51:09.943Z","parentId":"aee97cc8-952d-4a96-9a3c-866ad2c5bb4b"}
